data: The project will deliver a programme of business support to meet the needs of high-growth potential SMEs in creative/digital/business services/social enterprise sectors. Businesses across south-east and east London will benefit from academic expertise, leading to SME growth and job creation. The project offers value for money (VFM) compared to similar projects.
